Key features:
	- automatically groups tabs and bookmarks by content similarity;
	- manages tabs that have not been read for a long time according to user preferences;
	- reminds about "Read Later" bookmarks when you are reading similar article;
	- lightweight and private. No heavy AI, just pure algorithms that work in place, without data transfer.

Although it may look simple, and yet it is a powerful tool for boosting your productivity and fueling your creativity, that:
	- streamlines reading flow;
	- saves your time on relevant tab search and context switching;
	- helps to reveal implicit insights and story behind;
	- reduces cognitive load;
	- sparks new ideas by tying things together.

And more is yet to come. Stay tuned.

Tested for: English, Ukrainian, Russian.
Content in other languages may be partially supported.
